Coding tools required: HTML, JavaScript, CSS -- For website 
Kortlin, C++ -- For mobile app
OracleSQL -- For database management

Things to create:
1) A website for available and allocated ventilator information which is dynamic with time.
2) A mobile app which is user specific and hospital specific.

Flow:
--Hospitals have to upload data about how much ventilaters are in use and how many are free.
--We have to hire a B2B transport facility to transport the ventilater inter-hospitals where in need.
--Patients can see in which hospitals most no. of ventilators are vacant.
--In case of emergency ventilators can be transported between nearest hospitals.
--In this way the load on specific hospitals can be incresed.
